{"type": "article", "id": 43945, "title": "资生堂业绩大涨，以及，NMD 要出麂皮款 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-08-10T03:14:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 1653, "name": "Michael Kors"}, {"id": 2840, "name": "Opening Ceremony"}, {"id": 6419, "name": "Armani"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 21327, "name": "WTAPS"}, {"id": 27239, "name": "NMD"}, {"id": 1099, "name": "资生堂"}, {"id": 3803, "name": "Pandora"}, {"id": 43090, "name": "e.I.f Beauty"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170810100143TWjyEiXC0SuBV58z.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/457318\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>资生堂今年上半年的业绩表现不错，营业利润大涨了 73.9%</strong></a> | 截止至 6 月 30 日的上半年里，资生堂的销售额增长了 14.5%，至 4721 亿日元，其中营业利益大涨了 73.9%，至 346 亿日元。在中国市场，资生堂旗下的三个护肤品牌 SHISEIDO、Clé de Peau Beauté 和 IPSA 均有增长。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170809006045/en/e.l.f.-Beauty-Announces-Quarter-2017-Results\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>美国平价化妆连锁品牌 e.I.f Beauty 第二季度销售额大涨 27%</strong></a> | 今年第二季度， e.I.f Beauty 的销售额上涨了 27%，至 5590 万美元。得益于面向零售商的直接业务增长，e.I.f Beauty 的毛利率从 57% 扩大至 64%。</p><p><a href=\"http://luxe.co/post/65678\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>丹麦珠宝品牌 Pandora 第二季度销售额略低于预期，亚太地区大涨 35%</strong></a> | Pandora 在第二季度的销售额同比增长了 12%，达到 48.25 亿丹麦克朗，略低于分析师预期的 49 亿丹麦克朗。Pandora 在亚太地区表现抢眼，该地区销售额大涨 35%，至 10.72 亿丹麦克朗。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>携手美国潮牌集合店 Opening Ceremony，<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/08/09/vans-opening-ceremony-satin-pack/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vans 推出新联名系列 Satin Pack。 </a></p><p>该系列包括粉色、黄色、白色、黑色，鞋身特别选用了绸缎材质。它将于美国时间 8 月 11 日正式登陆 Opening Ceremony 旗舰店及网店，售价为 100 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100221fQ8OCm0xVevGUl5W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100214oKOxl0rSfW5PUqiL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100216HIBkjogmtwlvnu0R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708101002169Xg7BaunJk81ezb5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100221SdHbLY6coOuX9GDf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100228oHwJyNDWb0vEQLdp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100228p5A94cyZvfX7CLaV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://store.prada.com/SearchDisplay?back=&amp;searchTerm=fur+loafer&amp;q=fur%2520loafer&amp;storeId=10151&amp;langId=-1&amp;sType=SimpleSearch&amp;showResultsPage=true&amp;searchSourceQ=Q&amp;q1=fur+loafer&amp;searchTarget=store\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada</a> 2017 秋冬系列全毛皮莫卡辛鞋正式发售，定价 950 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100257Ugwj6vbqniaZpLdm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708101003056bWrmkKYGoE3IlVz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100320vq6elzRUpniL4E7d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100321mOzjtlhbB0gJPy19.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708101003216CvNtLQqoTF9rkBg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100321ZneLo26JWRGTK1kf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100325i9KsvrcUFDg3wHN2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100325eTorzIjpSHckNUGB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100320dDV3zc8inTPjoyrv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100332IrdKJ5ZaBuhlRWM9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100320XoTYu8shGnxWRQHc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100332b7Numh01k5AU4SWw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/balmain-launched-lipstick-collection-with-loreal/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Balmain 和 L’Oréal 的联名系列</a>很大胆。这次推出的 12 支哑光唇膏里，除了红色系的 Tribe Couture 之外，还有以咖啡色和卡其色为主的 Tribe Glamazone 系列，以及深咖、灰色、蓝色和紫色这样，对普通人实在是很不友好的 Tribe Rock 系列。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810101328qOncdN8MCfxTSYuK.png\" data-ratio=\"1.101824\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810101330Kc4W591dNgsjPrYI.png\" data-ratio=\"1.103343\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810101331kd4lAJh3jQ2TXFG6.png\" data-ratio=\"1.095890\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810101335NeindVKrObHkzY3D.png\" data-ratio=\"0.891933\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810101336TfExdhunNCzGWa8p.png\" data-ratio=\"1.097412\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>Michael Kors 推出了一个城市主题的 <a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-08-08/michael-kors-selma-novelty/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SELMA 系列</a>，首波新品包括东京、伦敦、巴黎、纽约四大都市，另外还有一款 Global 特别版。 </p><p>拼贴画和钉珠是怎么回事… 看起来真的不高级啊。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708101004404MINvpnjod0r1GTa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100447BQYdkPCnrxiHw58e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.345455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017081010044739sP6NOfrG50Fw4e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.345455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100447aiC9ZYVGvt0W1EBm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.345455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100451svROM5KtUoLh0wqS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.345455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100451KT8YPtCgc6ZUXAOn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.345455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>日本潮牌 WTAPS 联手 Herschel Supply Co，推出了以<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/wtaps-herschel-supply-co-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> SNEAK 为主题的联名系列</a>。 </p><p>该系列一共包括五个不同的款式，背包、斜肩包、拉链袋、洗漱包及零钱包，以高密度尼龙材质和数码迷彩图案共同打造，定价 27 至 200 美元不等，将于 8 月 11 日在 GIP-STORE 率先上架。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708101005161MfPQJtiYZ98yspK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100516wERLorvShTNCl7x4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100516u2ER8rBiMJSyf01T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100516onZa9CEiML6U5OGY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100516pUOs6WAdmnzFqEj2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100517W0clrmTE5dCZ8yqa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708101005176ZEFW3nXgVMKNQru.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100517TMgSfIBvzNrEnh0s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100517vsA8VHlk0KJ65qOw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100518MX2d9osLctOx1PIN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100518tia0pHksQXbR2oFd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100518w6OLsS10Izcp8TPF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100518s0bRhl2YV3dgmuEQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100518JDjr5GseX1LZ7wNy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100518DdG6XW1KZclVtiar.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100519KrGDRIHzXf4UyeAk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100519Q08V6CK2M4gho9pD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100519eaClrpqh8EtmLkwR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708101005208SNIOrkQmRy26V9u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>继巴黎、伦敦之后，阿玛尼的快闪店 <a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-08-09/armani-box/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Armani Box </a>来到了东京表参道 R Studio。在 9 月 2 日至 24 日期间，Armani Box 将会特别贩售一些新商品。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100536sBQy9iEVqbckCA7R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100536jp64iAQnVJT8OH0f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.601515\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100536PsMxyhfg1aNQe70r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100540etBJNHyF3hA5k8nc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100540n16NMxFeXrRBz0Ag.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>adidas 总是能换着花样地出新鞋。这次，<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/adidas-originals-nmd-r2-black-leather-white\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Originals 推出全新麂皮版 NMD R2</a> 鞋款，预计将于今年十月份正式发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100628A8s5g7Z1qwMW4HJI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708101006286m7aZWb9wTzsjPlL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170810100628FEiWBfDV1I8vMTmr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/08/09/vans-opening-ceremony-satin-pack/\" rel=\"nofollow\">highsnobiety</a></p>"}